WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.679 --> 00:00:10.530
Do you have something to say? A story that
needs to be told? A cause that needs to be

00:00:10.530 --> 00:00:19.730
heard? A local issue that needs to go global?
YouTube and the World Economic Forum are opening

00:00:19.730 --> 00:00:30.450
the doors of Davos to an individual, a big
thinker, a campaigner. You. To share the stage

00:00:30.450 --> 00:00:36.720
with world leaders in a special panel Dedicated
to your cause. Are you fighting for human

00:00:36.720 --> 00:00:47.100
rights? The environment? Poverty? Whatever
your cause, this is your chance to stand up

00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:55.190
and get your voice heard. Only one person
can join them. Someone with passion. With

00:00:55.190 --> 00:01:03.219
energy. With an urgent cause that needs the
world's attention. Press record, deliver your

00:01:03.219 --> 00:01:13.080
pitch, upload it to YouTube by Jan 4th 2010
for your chance to participate in the Davos

00:01:13.080 --> 00:01:19.650
Debates. Visit youtube.com/davos for more
details. If you had the chance to re-design

00:01:19.650 --> 00:01:21.480
your world, what would it look like?

